  "title": "Operations Supervisor",
  "description": "<p>Job requirement</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Able to liaise with Mandarin, Vietnamese, Myanmar speaking associates</li>\n  <li>Must have a least 1 year of experience in F&amp;B outlet, like food court, coffee shop and restaurant</li>\n  <li>Able to work long hours, weekend and public holiday</li>\n  <li>Assisting operation manager in daily operation, like roster planning, ordering of stock from supplier</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Description</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Comply with company's policies and procedures relating to all outlet activities</li>\n  <li>Perform mise-end place</li>\n  <li>Provide supervisor customer service that is fast, super friendly and customized to the needs of each customer</li>\n  <li>provide efficient, accurate preparation and sale of products for prompt customer service delivery in accordance to established SOP like taking customer order - clearing tables - require making coffee - perform cashiering at times - does mopping and cleaning of dining areas and dishwashing - any other duties which may be assigned from time to time.</li>\n</ul>",
